  "image_directives": "warm, candid dance-studio photography. Sprung floors, ballet barres, mirrors, tights and leotards mid-class. Kids in pre-ballet circles, teen jazz combos full-out, adult beginners trying a chasse for the first time. Real recital costumes backstage, dressing room moments, a teacher kneeling to fix a foot. Avoid pageant-pose competition stock, no glitter-overload hero shots, no airbrushed lines. Sweat on the marley, hair coming loose at the end of class.",
